]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the profane months."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.) And (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went forth to the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hil~", "text_ar": "حِلّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he became in the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hil~", "text_ar": "حِلّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; which means the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "region without the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haram", "text_ar": "حَرَم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sacred territory"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (Msb:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he became free from,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "quit of, an obligation"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of any kind"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that was upon him."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.) ―         -b2-  It is said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHil~a bimano A^aHal~a bika", "text_ar": "اَحِلَّ بِمَنْ اَحَلَّ بِكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Whoso quits the state of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iHoraAm", "text_ar": "اـِحْرَام"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and makes it lawful to attack thee, and fights with thee, do thou so with him, though thou be in the state of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHrAm", "text_ar": "احرام"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": or it means,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "if a man make lawful to him what is unlawful to him, as thy honour or reputation, and thy property, repel him from thyself in such a way as thou canst."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Sgh, TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHl~t", "text_ar": "احلّت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text"